outputs.output_descr:
The objective of this Joint Programme is to contribute to decreasing infant and maternal mortality in Kenya. This will be achieved through supporting the Beyond Zero campaign, an initiative of the First Lady of Kenya which aims at controlling HIV and promoting maternal , newborn and child health in Kenya by improving access to health care services. The campaign was launched under the leadership of the Ministry of Health (premised on Kenya's wider eMTCT Framework) and is to be anchored within the national political systems, devolved governance structures right down to the community level.
